<p>Then again, what the hell. Upvoted. I have suspended my disbelief for worse, the issue of range has provided some good narrativium and the whole thing is excellent.</p>
<p>One question: is &quot;the only non Omega-7 recovery&quot; case mentioned in the main text related to the separately-reported incident? Because as far as I can tell, the descriptions are inconsistent if so and the former is not the only such incident if not.</p>

